  "closes_issue": 939,
  "method": "reanalysis only (no Whisper / no ASR run); loads the EXACT same per-track feature matrix and mode labels from RQ23's mode_classifier_results.csv (677 tracks), augments the 5 original transcript features with 7 metadata features extracted from the AISHELL-4 validation windows (runtime_ratio, sep_total_chars, mix_total_chars, char_ratio, num_active_speakers_sep, avg_speaker_length_sep, length_entropy_speakers) plus a has_metadata binary indicator (0 for gold, 1 for AISHELL-4), and trains a numpy-only random forest identical to RQ28 (100 trees, max_depth=10, sqrt class weighting, LOO-CV).",
